{"tid":1660088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可唔可以用焦距解釋彥琳成日唔同樣？","createTime":"2019-10-17T10:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T11:44:50.000Z","uid":199800,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d3a4902b410e1fde9bd41fa517de2d1c4ed75fd","tid":1660088,"uid":199800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"連登好多po都話彥琳嘅自拍同cctv或者其他相個樣好唔同。咁假設cctv係真嘅，有無合理解釋點解明明同一個人，但係唔同相唔同樣呢？<br />\n<br />\n相信好多女仔都有過自己自拍明明好瘦好索但一影相就勁肥嘅困擾。我之前係網上睇到過d文章話，人像攝影之所以會出現呢種畸形現象，係因為鏡頭焦距嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n大家睇下呢幅圖：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4G62hzo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4G62hzo.png&h=7fc33e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖中嘅model係同一個人，但佢個樣係唔同焦距嘅鏡頭下係可以出現好大變異：焦距越細嘅鏡頭魚眼效應越強，五官越集中&amp;塊面越窄；而焦距越大嘅鏡頭就拉得個人越闊。<br />\n<br />\n我地再睇下陳彥琳嘅相（係第二位巴打嘅po借黎）：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dGFuG2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdGFuG2a.png&h=4d67930e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地可以見到彥琳嘅自拍有好明顯魚眼效應嘅特徵，而手機鏡頭嘅焦距確實比較細，係35mm，而最切合真實容貌嘅焦距係85mm，因此我覺得彥林個樣係唔同攝影器材中出現一定變化可以話係一個合理現象。<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指正。"},{"pid":"87c3d060d3de92475fa938a2368699fb20a26ca2","tid":1660088,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9f9f96cbcea585d510f1f0df775717a74e9df7fd","tid":1660088,"uid":199800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:04:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42c06c199c5acba1eb833acade9fc5e3704d5a7f","tid":1660088,"uid":199800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:06:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1eb0f39c23a223ea2c9daa943f2d6fef8fd575df","tid":1660088,"uid":199800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:08:29.